
How to generate API documentation
---------------------------------

Javascript doc:
	naturaldocs -i ~/spica2/terapix/media/js/ -i ~/spica2/terapix/templates/ -o HTML ~/tmp/spica2/api/js/ -p ~/tmp/spica2/api/prj/

Python doc:
	doxygen config.doxy

	Note: Python doc uses doxypy, an input filter for Doxygen. It preprocesses python files so that docstrings of 
	classes and functions are reformatted into Doxygen conform documentation blocks. 

	http://code.foosel.org/doxypy
